SELECT Program_Name, Age, MAX(Impact_Score) AS Max_Impact_Score FROM Monitoring_and_Evaluating_Programs p JOIN Program_Impact pi ON p.Program_ID = pi.Program_ID JOIN Program_Participants pp ON pi.Participant_ID = pp.Participant_ID WHERE Age >= 25 GROUP BY Program_Name, Age ORDER BY Max_Impact_Score DESC;
